    <item>
      <title>据称道达尔将以近 20 亿欧元收购可再生能源公司 VSB</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/total-said-to-near-2-billion-deal-for-renewable-developer-vsb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，道达尔能源公司 (TotalEnergies SE) 即将从私募股权公司 Partners Group Holding AG 手中收购 VSB 集团，该交易对这家德国可再生能源项目开发商的估值约为 20 亿欧元（21 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/total-said-to-near-2-billion-deal-for-renewable-developer-vsb</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:50:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
